</para><para>
Any output on one view is duplicated in the other view.
</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term><menuchoice>
<shortcut><keycombo action="simul">&Ctrl;<keycap>)</keycap></keycombo></shortcut>
